# ======================================================
# RISC-Plunne - Gitignore
# ======================================================

# Ignore everything by default
*

# ------------------------------------------------------
# Git essentials
# ------------------------------------------------------
!.gitignore
!README.md
!LICENSE

# -----------------------------
# Include Documentation
# -----------------------------
!Docs/
!Docs/**

# -----------------------------
# Include Blog
# -----------------------------
!Blog/
!Blog/**

# -----------------------------
# Include Vivado project
# -----------------------------
!Sources/
!Sources/*.xpr

# -----------------------------
# Include RTL sources
# -----------------------------
!Sources/rtl/
!Sources/rtl/**

# -----------------------------
# Include Simulation sources
# -----------------------------
!Sources/sim/
!Sources/sim/**

# ======================================================
# Notes:
# 1) Everything not explicitly included above is ignored
# 2) All Vivado generated files are excluded
#    automatically 
# 3) New RTL or TB files under rtl/ or sim/ are tracked
#    automatically
# ======================================================